<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Tree Donation Certificate</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .main{
            height: 98vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-evenly;
            align-items: center;  
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .certificate {
            max-width: 700px;
            /* margin: px auto; */
            background-color: #d3d3d33d;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            flex-direction: column;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            /* flex-shrink: ; */
        }

        h1 {
            background-image: url(https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1541701494587-cb58502866ab?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D);
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            background-clip: text;
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            color: transparent;
            -webkit-text-stroke: 1px #4CAF50;
            font-size: 2em;
            font-weight: bolder;
            margin: 10px 10px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }

        .donation-amount {
            font-size: 1.5em;
            color: #4CAF50;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .footer {
            /* max-width: 700px; */
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            padding: 1em;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 10px;
            /* position: fixed;
            bottom: 0; */
            /* max-width: 800px; */
            /* margin: 0px 20px;   */
        }

        @media (300px <= width <= 600px) {
          .certificate{
            /* max-width: 500px; */
            /* background-color: aqua; */
            padding: 10px;
            margin: 20px 10px;
          
          }
          p{
            font-size: 14px;
            margin: 10px 0;
          }
          body{
            height: 80%;
          }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="main">

      <div class="certificate">
        <h1>Tree Donation Certificate</h1>
        <p>This certifies that</p>
        <p><span class="donor-name"><%= Name%></span></p>
        <p>has generously donated the amount of</p>
        <p class="donation-amount">$<%= Amount %></p>
        <p>for planting <span class="tree-count">5</span> trees.</p>
        <p>Thank you for your commitment to a greener and healthier planet!</p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>Â© 2023 Tree Plantation Organization. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

</body>

</html>
